==== Show ====
Click the <tt>Show</tt> link to go to the details page for the associated connection.  Each connection's page includes the Name, Title, and Description for each of the items that the connection references.

==== Edit ====
Click the <tt>Edit</tt> link to go to the <tt>Edit</tt> page for the associated connection.  A connection's <tt>Edit</tt> page allows the items which the connection references to be changed, or a new item for the connection to reference to be created.

==== Delete ====
Click the <tt>Delete</tt> link to remove the associated connection from the system.  When clicked, <tt>Delete</tt> will cause a dialog box to be displayed, asking you to confirm that you want the connection permanently removed.
